microservice.infrastructure.controllers.internal

Class InternalController

  • java.lang.Object
    • microservice.infrastructure.controllers.internal.InternalController

  • @Controller
 @CrossOrigin(origins="*")
 @RequestMapping(value="/")
public class InternalController
extends java.lang.Object
    Only requests made on the service port are valid to the controller This controller handles all internal communication, from infrastructure to microservices
